&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="33-q3-compile-error">&lt;a href="#33-q3-compile-error" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>3.3 Q3: Compile error
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="331-a">&lt;a href="#331-a" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>3.3.1 A:
